<p>HVAC contractors waste 6-8 weeks onboarding each new technician using outdated training methods. Meanwhile, existing techs need 16-24 continuing education hours annually to maintain their licenses, and NATE certification pass rates hover around 65% without proper preparation.</p>

<p>Online HVAC training platforms solve these problems by delivering structured, trackable education that reduces onboarding time by 50% and increases certification pass rates to 85-90%. After reviewing 23 platforms and surveying 200+ HVAC contractors, here are the best options for different company needs.</p>
